the proximal functions,

00:31:06.910 --> 00:31:07.900
and ultimate functions.

00:31:07.900 --> 00:31:10.580
Ultimate functions are why we,
as a species, do these things.

00:31:10.580 --> 00:31:12.240
And they're the
ultimate benefits.

00:31:12.240 --> 00:31:15.150
But the idea is, if we do these
things for proximal reasons

00:31:15.150 --> 00:31:16.987
