good about myself,

00:31:16.987 --> 00:31:18.820
that's enough of a
proximal reason to do it.

00:31:18.820 --> 00:31:20.420
That gets you to
do the behaviors.

00:31:20.420 --> 00:31:23.040
The ultimate outcome is you're
going to get high status.

00:31:23.040 --> 00:31:24.070
But you don't have
to worry about that.

00:31:24.070 --> 00:31:25.490
Evolution has made
