00:33:19.726 --> 00:33:21.350
JESSICA TRACY: That's
a great question.

00:33:21.350 --> 00:33:24.170
So I would say that
they're very similar.

00:33:24.170 --> 00:33:26.100
Authentic pride, I
would say, is very much

00:33:26.100 --> 00:33:28.417
a sense of self-confidence.

00:33:28.417 --> 00:33:30.000
Typically, we think
of self-confidence

00:33:30.000 --> 00:33:32.720
more as a disposition, so a
trait that some people have

00:33:32.720 --> 00:33:34.470
and some people don't,
