00:33:34.470 --> 00:33:36.070
a lot and some
people have less of.

00:33:36.070 --> 00:33:37.570
And authentic
pride, we can think

00:33:37.570 --> 00:33:39.650
of more as a momentary
state for the most

00:33:39.650 --> 00:33:41.670
part, although we
can be dispositional

00:33:41.670 --> 00:33:42.827
authentically proud.

00:33:42.827 --> 00:33:44.660
If your dispositionally
authentically proud,

00:33:44.660 --> 00:33:47.110
I would say that's much the
same as having a strong sense

00:33:47.110 --> 00:33:47.922
