00:33:47.922 --> 00:33:49.670
But what I think is
important is the way

00:33:49.670 --> 00:33:50.734
that we use these terms.

00:33:50.734 --> 00:33:52.650
Sometimes, when we talk
about self-confidence,

00:33:52.650 --> 00:33:54.550
we don't distinguish
between what

00:33:54.550 --> 00:33:56.690
I would call the
authentic pride and more

00:33:56.690 --> 00:33:58.450
