00:34:05.797 --> 00:34:08.213
And I think that's a really
important distinction to make.

00:34:08.213 --> 00:34:10.100
So I like using the
term "self-confident,"

00:34:10.100 --> 00:34:13.880
but I want to be clear about
saying, well, self-confidence,

00:34:13.880 --> 00:34:16.639
to me, is confidence in your
hard work and achievements

00:34:16.639 --> 00:34:17.679
and productivity.

00:34:17.679 --> 00:34:18.590
It's authentic pride.

00:34:18.590 --> 00:34:20.692
It's not this grandiose
sense of self.

00:34:20.692 --> 00:34:22.607
Sure.

