you've decided, that's pride.

00:36:23.380 --> 00:36:25.905
Pride is what makes you want
to feel good about yourself.

00:36:25.905 --> 00:36:26.780
It's not a bad thing.

00:36:26.780 --> 00:36:27.571
It's not bad pride.

00:36:27.571 --> 00:36:28.610
It's not arrogance.

00:36:28.610 --> 00:36:30.860
It is just authentic pride.

00:36:30.860 --> 00:36:34.080
And as humans, we evolved
to have the sense of self

00:36:34.080 --> 00:36:35.170
that we care deeply about.

00:36:35.170 --> 00:36:37.080
And there's an enormous
adaptive advantages

00:36:37.080 --> 00:36:39.630
