understand that we're not

00:36:55.850 --> 00:36:56.850
talking about arrogance.

00:36:56.850 --> 00:36:58.060
We're not talking about egotism.

00:36:58.060 --> 00:36:59.893
We're not talking about
putting others down,

00:36:59.893 --> 00:37:01.940
